data.description: Brand-new home for sale in Lakeland, Florida. This is a professionally decorated model home finishes, as well as furniture, do not convey. May be purchased at additional cost. The spacious Westin features a popular open layout with a spacious gathering room, open kitchen, and formal and casual dining spaces. Relax in your luxurious owner's suite with an elegant tray ceiling, walk-in wardrobe, and spa-like owner's bath with garden tub and an oversized tiled shower with glass enclosure, dual vanities, linen closet, and closeted toilet.  This home includes many stylish finishes and low-maintenance features:  Open kitchen with:  Premium, low maintenance laminate countertops with a crescent edge finish Cotton painted cabinets with soft close, crown moulding, and decorative knobs/pulls  Samsung stainless steel smooth-top range, over-the-range microwave, and quiet-operation dishwasher, and side by side refrigerator Pull-down faucet  Energy-efficient LED recessed lighting  Large breakfast bar  Walk-in pantry with tight mesh shelving  On-trend wood vinyl plank flooring  Stylish and low maintenance wood vinyl plank flooring throughout the cafe/nook, foyer, den, laundry room, and bathrooms  Mohawk stain-resistant carpet  Samsung full-size front load washer, and dryer Wireless security system and sound system 2-in custom-fit faux-wood blinds throughout Screened enclosed lanai Ceiling fan and cable prewire in the gathering room & bedroom  SELLER TO PAY ALL CLOSING COSTS WITH OUR PREFERRED LENDERS!
